Name: # Safe Name for us
Type: Type of block, not sure what options there are here?
State: The state (SOLID, LIQUID, GAS), probably used to create the block/liquid?
Rarity: The rarity, don't know how this will be used?
Spawn_Rate: We can tweak the spawning at world gen. Not sure on a "normal" level. Aluminium is pretty abundant?
Radioactive: Is it radioactive? If TRUE it will damage the palyer
ItemName: The item dropped (the block name unless different)
Generate_Ore: Should the Ore be generated? Leaves room for "experimental" elements that can only be obtained.
Texture: The texture name. Leave blank for a liquid

Texture_moving: The "moving" texture for a liquid. Leave blank for block.

OreName: The ore name for the block (ores only of course). Leave blank for gasses/fluids
